 His wife died 2 years ago and he still spends a lot of time thinking about
 her.
 He has 4 children and 10 grandchildren who visit him regularly.
 John can make ends meet but has no money for extras such as expensive gifts
 to his grandchildren.
 He has had to stop working recently due to heart problems.
 He gets tired easily.
 Otherwise, he has no serious health conditions.
 How satisfied with his life do you think John is? 
\end_layout

